comments: Not an Easy A, i dont think any language is. But as far as taching danish is concerned, Kevin is the teacher to learn it from. Show up to class or you will miss something important. Always do your homework as well. It will make the class so much easier and way more fun.
This class changed my life. I\'d never studied about the Danes before, but now I know more about them than I do about America! Mi gusta hablar Danish!
